<title>外交部提醒：春节期间避免前往日本！</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%A5%E8%8A%82%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%89%8D%E5%BE%80%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%EF%BC%81</link>
